text: Britské listy is an Internet cultural and political daily published in the Czech Republic. It specialises in critical analysis of Czech politics; some Czech commentators consider this as "left-wing views". It is editorially open and will publish stimulating pieces by authors from any part of the political spectrum == Other websites == * Britské listy * Focus on the Czech Republic (The best of Czech daily Britské listy) Category:Czech Republic Category:Politics of Europe Category:Newspapers in Europe
